Export.zv: Cache for UNIX (Red Hat Enterprise Linux for x86-64) 2014.1.3 (Build 775)

Method.name: %OnSaveSource
Method.Implementation: Set tSC = pSource.%Save() Set ..%id = pSource.%Id() Quit tSC

Method.name: %OnLoadModel
Method.Implementation: Set ..EDStatus = pSource.EDStatus Set ..WaitTime = pSource.WaitTime Set ..Color = pSource.Color Set ..NotifyMgr = pSource.NotifyMgr Set ..NotifyByEmail = pSource.NotifyByEmail Set ..NotifyByPager = pSource.NotifyByPager Set ..StartTm = pSource.StartTm Set ..EndTm = pSource.EndTm Quit $$$OK

Method.name: %OnStoreModel
Method.Implementation: Set pSource.EDStatus = ..EDStatus Set pSource.WaitTime = ..WaitTime Set pSource.Color = ..Color Set pSource.NotifyMgr = ..NotifyMgr Set pSource.NotifyByEmail = ..NotifyByEmail Set pSource.NotifyByPager = ..NotifyByPager Set pSource.StartTm = ..StartTm Set pSource.EndTm = ..EndTm Quit pSource.%Save()
